{
  "stem": "3380.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "From Weimar-- this is part of-- of Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When we came into Weimar, we couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We couldn't-- the trains couldn't get in because the Americans bombed the railroad, so we couldn't get in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we went in marching in to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When we came to Buchenwald, my brother Sam was very sick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He got frozen legs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "His feet was frozen, and he was in terrible pain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he begged me that I should go on, that I should save myself.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I said, no, this-- as long I will be able to go, you will be able to go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I took him out in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He couldn't walk, so I carried him into the block.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Waited three, four days to get in because everybody tried to get in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But after you get the [? bat, ?] then you got something to eat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But I didn't left Sam alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We took him-- I took when he was sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He just could not step on his feet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So I carried him on my shoulders, and I took him into block-- block 57 in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he was there, and I was being.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "In the same block was a part like three bunks for-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was allocated for the sick people, and that was a doctor there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he was there-- he was laying there sick that-- they couldn't do-- they didn't have any medical-- [NON-ENGLISH] they didn't have any medicine for it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he was in pain, and I tried to go and tried to help him as much as he can-- as-- as-- as much as I can.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the doctor got a liking to me, and he said to me that I should help him, what would help.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
